scheme2c (1993.3.15.2-11) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * bump standards version (debian/control)
  * add useful utilities to package
    - scxl.a (X library for linking to) and associated *.sch include files
    - cdecl (generate C declarations from Scheme code, for linking) as s2cdecl
    - sch (generate C headers, for linking external C)
    - scixl (interpreter with X procedures available)
    - sizeof.cdecl (standard sizes on current architecture)
  * debhelper 8
  * accept armhf patch to debian/control and debian/rules (closes: #604665)
  * allow parallel build (debian/rules)
  * merge upstream changes: increase AMD64 max heap size and ditch gensym

 -- Barak A. Pearlmutter <bap@debian.org>  Fri, 11 Mar 2011 10:54:37 +0000

